{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 3,
  "title": "第三章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "不尚賢，使民不爭；不貴難得之貨，使民不為盜；不見可欲，使民心不亂。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人之治，虛其心，實其腹，"
    },
    {
      "text": "弱其志，強其骨。"
    },
    {
      "text": "常使民無知無欲。"
    },
    {
      "text": "使夫智者不敢為也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "為無為，則無不治。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 33
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "賢，猶能也。尚者，嘉之名也。貴者，隆之稱也。唯能是任，尚也曷為；唯用是施，貴之何為。尚賢顯名，榮過其任，為而常校，能相射貴貨，過用貪者，競趣穿窬探篋，沒命而盜，故可欲不見，則心無所亂也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "心懷智而腹懷食，虛有智而實無知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "骨無知以幹，志生事以亂，心虛則志弱也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "守其真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "知者謂知為也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
